{"tid":1988193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣區議會動議將大河道一號休憩處命名「10.1港人抗暴花園」","createTime":"2020-04-25T04:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:36:09.000Z","uid":24070,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"63e61fc57593204de2dd23cbdf4490090c766fc4","tid":1988193,"uid":24070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"荃灣區議會已通過將大河道一號休憩處命名為「10.1港人抗暴花園」，但康文署稱不接受，各位手足麻煩幫手上Google Map改名，反映民意！<br />\n<br />\n中文： 10.1港人抗暴花園<br />\n英文： 10.1 Hongkonger Anti Police Brutality Garden<br />\n<br />\n//議員動議命名「抗暴花園」警方突離席<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議會今日亦討論動議將大河道一號休憩處命名為「10.1港人抗暴花園」，多名議員均支持動議，提出動議的趙恩來稱，去年10月1日示威活動期間，有中學生被警方以實彈射擊胸部，希望透過花園命名，讓港人毋忘警暴。<br />\n<br />\n多名議員均支持議案，認為要令當權者警惕，但原本在席的兩名警務處代表，荃灣警區指揮官甘榮耀和警民關係主任古樂霖，在該議程前突然離開座位，民政專員葉錦菁則仍然在席。有議員質疑為何此議題可在會議討論，但另外2個動議被DQ，葉未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n最終有關動議獲得通過，但康文署代表稱，因該休憩處的命名已刊憲，而署方就設施命名有既定指引，一般都是以附近地標或設施等為休憩處進行命名，而署方已備悉議員意見，但有關動議的命名，並不符合當局命名原則，故署方不會接受。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mg3rZsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmg3rZsi.jpg&h=705cca6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YA6LGRYAWSHYSDHHCJ2SRBWKRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYA6LGRYAWSHYSDHHCJ2SRBWKRU%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e005a07f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYA6LGRYAWSHYSDHHCJ2SRBWKRU%2F&h=7ab19a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YA6LGRYAWSHYSDHHCJ2SRBWKRU/</a>"},{"pid":"834e3a28a3b45cbb8c0f1648bfa57dcd9f5a87d6","tid":1988193,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ee118768cd97a598ef661c50f272829c30504e9f","tid":1988193,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"Done"},{"pid":"6f0361181931dcac7526ddf0cbc352b63bfd8caa","tid":1988193,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"區議會真係唔夠<br />\n<br />\n摒棄幻想 準備奪權"},{"pid":"9b836aefbe59023c9a53c81a01c05f9a7525b313","tid":1988193,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"最終有關動議獲得通過，但康文署代表稱，因該休憩處的命名已刊憲，而署方就設施命名有既定指引，一般都是以附近地標或設施等為休憩處進行命名，而署方已備悉議員意見，但有關動議的命名，並不符合當局命名原則，故署方不會接受。<br />\n<br />\n咁咪改做「大河道1號 - 10.1 抗暴之地」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa11ed367d0f3f06a8c91a9ba252ac6d39096129","tid":1988193,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"學中國咁，改一堆起義路、解放路、建國路，睇下邊個咁唔愛國反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f0bf9f4c44ead83e03a78f024ee521f51ee184","tid":1988193,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4170fde8b9c8c23a7d8013bb3a0aae5bf8ca1a","tid":1988193,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85f527dca61517efe7a68533010e5f3e7e7e8d9","tid":1988193,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"區議會好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通過都可以唔做"},{"pid":"71f0ee2be7f63391c4b532d3c2f024d42f6382a8","tid":1988193,"uid":205469,"